
INSTALLATION
============

  You need OCaml >= 4.07.0 and Frama-C v18.0 to compile the sources.

  0. Generate configuration script with "autoconf".

  1. Configure with "./configure".

  2. Compile with "make".

  3. Install with "make install".  You may need superuser permissions.


If you are willing to use Coq (more precisely if Coq is detected when
running ./configure), you need Coq >= 8.7.

